title: Coconut Kahlua Cake
ingredients: ['520g sponge cake mix', '2 1/2 teaspoons instant coffee granules', '300ml coffee flavoured liqueur, such as Kahlua, divided', '475ml milk', '140g instant vanilla dessert mix, such as Angel Delight', '375ml whipping cream', '3 tablespoons caster sugar', '225g desiccated coconut']
